messages.text: Hey, we're going to call Amazon from Schrodinger

Otherwise I can wait for <@U3AF7DXEY> to get in, and check with him.

Yes, we have set that up much better to support that use case

We have done it in the past, and its not all that much work, its just not a well built solution right now because I need to set the email in the code and do a production release.
